criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  early rheumatoid arthritis fulfilment of the 2010 ACR/EULAR RA classification
             criteria;

          -  age between 18-65 years;

          -  female gender,

          -  naive for treatment.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  use of oral > 10 mg/d glucocorticoid in the previous three weeks;

          -  serum aspartate aminotransferase or alanine aminotransferase level > 3 times the upper
             limit of normal;

          -  bone marrow, auto-imune, lymphoproliferative or infectious diseases;

          -  pregnancy.
